ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This course provide you with an overall view of how cryo-EM works and what's its application in studying biological molecules. If you want to do structure biology in the future, this course will be quite helpful for you.
Yes. Everyone interested in biological research should definitely take advantage of this excellent class to learn about this technique of choice for examining large molecular complexes.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: In the future, I might use cryo-EM for a supplement to my structure biology research. Therefore, this course provide a good platform for introducing me into this field.
